      "title": "Petition against the 22nd Amendment",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "9 petitions have been filed in the High Court seeking to declare that certain clauses in the 22nd Amendment of the Constitution presented by the Government in the Parliament are unconstitutional.",
        "This petition has been filed by 9 citizens including lawyer Naganananda Kodithuvaku and doctor Gunadasa Amarasekara and the attorney general has been named as the respondent."
